### 게임 세션 생성 (문제 출제를 위해 필요)
POST {{memory_api}}/api/v1/game/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "gameMode": "RANDOM"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("session_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

